                                </h3>
                            </div>
                            <span
                                class="transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180"
                            >
                                <i
                                    class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down text-blue-600"
                                ></i>
                            </span>
                        </summary>
                        <div
                            class="px-6 pb-6 pt-0 ml-12 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed"
                        >
                            <p>
                                We adhere to a strict 60-minute replacement
                                guarantee. In case of a mechanical failure or
                                driver unavailability, a backup vehicle is
                                dispatched immediately to ensure your operations
                                continue.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </details>

                    <!-- FAQ 7 -->
                    <details
                        class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 overflow-hidden"
                    >
                        <summary
                            class="flex items-center justify-between p-6 cursor-pointer list-none"
                        >
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                                <div
                                    class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm"
